creator: Woke Enterprises LLC
descriptionHtml:
Are you ready to quit juuling? Ain't no motivation quite like saving money and, of course, your life! Kick the addiction, improve your health, and spare your wallet (cha-ching!). This app tracks the number of days your lungs are smoke-free and how much money you have saved so you can put those dollars toward something better! New shoes, perhaps? Your degree? Extra guac?

This simple app works for anyone who has (and is eager to stop using) a pod-based e-cigarette vape, such as:

+ JUUL
+ myBlu
+ SMOK Nord
+ UWELL Caliburn
+ Suorin Edge
+ VLADDIN RE

It's time to escape the vape...you in?
descriptionShort: Quit Juuling - Habit Tracker

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Didn't think it could get any better? Well, it just did! We now have more information so you can learn how your health is improving and why exactly nicotine is so d*mn addictive.

Don't think Juuling is bad for you? Don't listen to us - read the real life stories of many teens and young adults who have died or been hospitalized. One of these stories will kill your craving, real fast.

Have feature requests? Hit us up at team@escapethevape.co! We make updates every week.
